This layer provides support for Rugged Board A5d2x
==================================================

For more information about the rugged board a5d2x product line see:
https://www.ruggedboard.com/

Linux, development & Open Source on rugged board:
https://developer.ruggedboard.com/

Sources
=======
- meta-rba5d2x
URI: https://github.com/mohseen-ahamad/meta-rba5d2x.git
Branch: main

Dependencies
============
This Layer depends on :

- poky
URI: https://github.com/mohseen-ahamad/poky.git
Branch:main

- meta-openembedded
URI: git://git.openembedded.org/meta-openembedded
URI: http://cgit.openembedded.org/meta-openembedded/
Branch: sumo

Build procedure
===============

0/ Create a directory
mkdir my_dir
cd my_dir

1/ Clone yocto/poky git repository with the proper branch ready
git clone https://github.com/mohseen-ahamad/poky.git -b main

2/ Clone meta-openembedded git repository with the proper branch ready
git clone git://git.openembedded.org/meta-openembedded -b sumo

3/ Clone meta-rba5d2x layer with the proper branch ready
git clone https://github.com/mohseen-ahamad/meta-rba5d2x.git -b main

5/ Enter the poky directory to configure the build system and start the build process
cd ../

6/ Initialize build directory
source oe-init-build-env build-microchip

7/ Edit local.conf to specify the target machine and build the image
	i) For rugged board a5d2x(SDCARD)
    		-> Change machine name to "rugged-board-a5d2x-sd1" in conf/local.conf as below 
			MACHINE ?= "rugged-board-a5d2x-sd1"

    			$ bitbake rb-sd-core-image-minimal

Typical bitbake output
======================
Build Configuration:
BB_VERSION           = "1.38.0"
BUILD_SYS            = "x86_64-linux"
NATIVELSBSTRING      = "universal"
TARGET_SYS           = "arm-poky-linux-gnueabi"
MACHINE              = "rugged-board-a5d2x-sd1"
DISTRO               = "poky"
DISTRO_VERSION       = "2.5.3"
TUNE_FEATURES        = "arm armv7a vfp thumb neon callconvention-hard cortexa5"
TARGET_FPU           = "hard"
meta                 
meta-poky            
meta-yocto-bsp       = "main:6ae581677cf34e440e2c65ae41bb009236162213"
meta-rba5d2x-sumo    = "main:547f09ac46ea0c7fd9a7b9bc4516a8c5d124e01c"

Known issues
============
This branch is under development and not fully tested. Some features may not work.
